OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA settled
OL,6,Fand clear night to come with gusty
OL,7,Fwinds to start with but easing through
OL,8,Fthe night. Cloud approaching by dawn.
OL,9,FStaying relatively mild with some
OL,10,Fplaces staying in double figures,
OL,11,Fchillier in the far east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAfter a bright start, cloud
OL,14,Fbecoming more widespread through the
OL,15,Fmorning with showery outbreaks of rain
OL,16,Fin the west. Isolated thunderstorms
OL,17,Fpossible later in the day. Feeling
OL,18,Fwarm and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
